description:
Welcome to the world of Professional Advanced Kickball!

You know, kickball—it's like baseball only with kicking and there's nobody better at it than Rocky Hallelujah! Rocky and his ragtag team of kickballers have had a rough but successful year working their way towards the International ADV Kickball Championship. But when Rocky is faced with the biggest game of his career will he be up for the challenge? Will he choke or will he kick it squarely in the balls?

It's the newest "arcade logic" creation from the mind of Corey Sutherland Lewis-- "The Rey", creator of the smash hit Sharknife!

Featuring special guest appearances by characters from Sharknife!
